getDiscountedTotalPrice(uint256,uint256).notice: Discounted price for which should be specific for NFT owners

getTotalPrice(uint256,uint256).notice: calculates total price for given amount of tickets

removeSaloon(uint256,uint256).notice: removes the theatre with the given ID from the system

removeTheatre(uint256).notice: removes the theatre with the given ID from the system

updateTicketPrice(uint256,uint256).notice: Updates ticket prices for a particular theatre. No need for decimals

withdrawBalances().notice: Withdraws all theatre balances to owner's address. Only the owner can call the function
